@startuml
autonumber
actor "CRM Collaborator" as CRM
participant "System" as S

activate CRM
CRM -> S: Initiates adding drone models to a proposal.
activate S
S --> CRM: Displays list of proposals and available drone models.
deactivate S

CRM -> S: Selects proposal, drone models, and specifies quantities.
activate S
S --> CRM: Confirms the drone models have been added to the proposal.
deactivate S
deactivate CRM
@enduml